            <p style="margin-top: 10px">
                Abai was born in Karauyl village in Chingiz volost of Semipalatinsk
            </p>
            <p style="margin-top: 10px">
                He was the son of Qunanbai and Uljan, his father's second wife.
            </p>
            <p style="margin-top: 10px">
