            <h4 style="margin-top: auto; width: 490px">
                Abai's major work is The Book of Words (Qara sozderi),
                a theological philosophic treatise and collection of poems where he
                encourages his fellow Kazakhs to embrace education, literacy, and
                good moral character in order to escape poverty, enslavement and
                corruption.
